% -------------------- Projects --------------------
\section*{Projects}

\textbf{Analog Modular Synthesizer — Custom PCB and Signal Design} \hfill \textit{Analog Signals, PCB Design, Op-Amps, Power rails}

\begin{itemize}
    \item Designed voltage-controlled oscillators, filters, and amplifiers using op-amps and wave-shaping circuits on a custom low-noise PCB, reducing signal noise and crosstalk by \textbf{>60\%} compared to breadboard-based designs.
    
    \item Built dual-rail power regulation and grounding architecture with decoupling and filtering using LTspice simulations, PCB layout in KiCad, and precision measurement with oscilloscope and multimeter, lowering power ripple to <5 mV and ensuring stable, studio-grade audio output under load.

\end{itemize}

